This page lists all '''armour''' and other wearable equipment: armour sets, cloaks, bags and jewelry. Chest pieces, leggings, boots and gloves raise your [[Gear Level]] and grant stat bonuses; matching pieces add a set bonus.

==All armour and equipment==
Every piece of equipment on the wiki, drawn automatically from each page's infobox. Click a column header to sort — by gear level to see progression, or by type to compare jewelry and bags. Set details and crafting costs are in the sections below.
<div class="vr-table-scroll">
{{#cargo_query:tables=equipment
|fields=_pageName=Equipment,type=Type,gear_level=Gear level,stats=Stats,set_bonus=Set bonus,durability=Durability
|order by=gear_level DESC,_pageName
|limit=200
|format=table
}}
</div>

